units		metal
atom_style	atomic
newton on
thermo 1

boundary f f f
read_data structure.data

pair_style	allegro
pair_coeff	* * deployed-frozen.pth C O H
mass            1 12
mass            2 15.9994
mass            3 1.00794

velocity	all create 1000.0 376847 loop geom

neighbor	1.0 bin
neigh_modify    delay 5 every 1

fix		1 all nve

timestep	0.001

compute atomicenergies all pe/atom
compute totalatomicenergy all reduce sum c_atomicenergies

thermo_style custom step time temp pe c_totalatomicenergy etotal press spcpu cpuremain

run 0
write_dump all custom output.dump id type x y z fx fy fz modify sort id

